  "title": "美联储杀人，AI 埋尸？牛津曝光 L 型死局：10 亿打工人再无归路",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652667926&idx=2&sn=dcbeefa83632b326a71cb2ab3f523e63",
  "date": "2026-01-27 00:10:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.42643923240938164\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2345\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505184275\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c838d50&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo850usDibkMqiaYKlqNAtb1V9Iwf1hXuLk4R7DP9dicYT4HIwTGWnTkH7EA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">这是一份迟到三年的行业复盘。牛津大学最新的实证研究撕开了那层遮羞布：2022年全球科技大裁员爆发时，ChatGPT甚至尚未发布。周期性缩编被伪装成技术性迭代，AI替资本背了三年的锅，直到今天真相才被彻底复位。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一场幻觉，竟然持续了三年！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2022年11月，ChatGPT横空出世，随后硅谷开启大裁员，程序员和写手哀鸿遍野。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所有人都觉得，因为AI来了，所以我们失业了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，一项由牛津大学和基尔世界经济研究所团队发布的论文却告诉我们，我们恨错了人！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3825701624815362\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1354\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1354\" data-height=\"518\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"215\" data-imgfileid=\"505184065\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd63b91a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8xPMwmtWIoVrkZO8jVaItic1Ad0YMicCiaNcJL6Wiaaw5dZeU7aJ19IicDew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文地址：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.02554\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.02554</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实早在ChatGPT上线半年前，这些行业的需求已呈现断崖式下跌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那时，OpenAI还在调GPT-3.5的参数，根本没有功夫抢你的工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然如此，到底谁才是幕后真凶？又是谁让AI成了替罪羊？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一场持续3年的「集体幻觉」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果真如传言中那样，2022年的岗位需求应该在11月之后断崖式下跌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，数据显示，下跌其实早就开始了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"144\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"84\" data-imgfileid=\"505184064\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8474b580&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8RoJw8zPMC2keCKB1WhwfBwsREz1yibqupo8SJ77xfPJicThANDaKbxqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">计算机、商务、金融等高AI暴露率的职业，其失业风险在2022上半年已远超餐饮与建筑业。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这会儿，奥特曼还在为算力账单发愁，ChatGPT甚至没有出生。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，我们不能贸然将失业和AI划等号，就像你无法指控未出世的婴儿杀了人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了进一步验证以防误伤，研究团队开始了一场对照试验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实验组是科技依赖型岗位。2022年上半年，随着「远程办公泡沫」破裂，LinkedIn数据显示远程职位申请竞争度飙升，但招聘需求却从2022年初的峰值开始滑坡。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对照组是非科技依赖型工作，如餐饮、护理等在同一时间不仅没有崩盘，反而因为「后疫情复苏」出现了严重的用工荒。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4734375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 562px;height: 266px;\" data-width=\"1288\" data-height=\"626\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8n1pW1eTlicYGPRC4yR0Llhnpl41SjYqyicxDTYutDeh6Hyh1Qy0vNqzw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1288\" data-cropy1=\"16.04270462633452\" data-cropy2=\"625.6654804270463\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"273\" data-imgfileid=\"505184066\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58f2aec9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8WLGMNgGheGjmaiaU85UPz0gYCicibe57jd30LiaezldPb9KjKKPIjUqhow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">不同职业从的失业风险变化，颜色的深浅表示职业的暴露度。颜色越深，暴露度越高</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说GPT的出现取代了人类的工作，那么最开始取代的也应该是低级脑力工作，高级技能岗位依旧保留。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但数据显示的结果是无差别的行业雪崩。不论你是初级码农还是资深架构师，只要身处科技与外包行业，均被无差别清洗。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就说明，受害者是按照行业资金充裕度划定的，而不是「是否能被AI替代」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，杀死工作的凶手，肯定不是当时的GPT-3.5，它只是经过，就成了替罪羊。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">杀死你的不是算法，是周期</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然GPT只是替罪羊，那么，凶手到底是谁？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果一定要指名道姓，那么凶手应当是美联储主席Jerome Powell，或者说，是那时的宏观周期。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让我们看向更早的时间点——2021年。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那是一个疯狂的年份，全球疫情导致物理隔绝，科技公司以为这种数字化繁荣将成为常态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">于是，巨头和独角兽们开启了一场史无前例的「抢人大战」，钱也慢慢变得不值钱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">只要你会写代码、会画图、甚至只要简历上沾点「数字化」，你就能拿到溢价50%的Offer。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5622222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"900\" data-height=\"506\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505184068\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f685eb9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8YLibQEwWzZpb0BaytLGl5mA6Jyibiak6icUDdP2HicYBKwibC9icDYRwvnxbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">转折点发生在2022年年初，美联储开启暴力加息周期，全球风险投资瞬间腰斩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据Crunchbase的统计数据，2022年第三季度的全球风投融资额仅为810亿美元，同比暴跌53%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6994906621392191\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2356\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2356\" data-height=\"1648\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"393\" data-imgfileid=\"505184067\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06642abb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8t2k8XSpYqC21z2W9oUjwO5yUJSeu6oMgdnNtI5Ej99MUj9xCNnk6Rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">市场上流动的「抢人预算」在一夜之间蒸发了一半。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI只是其中的原因之一，更多是因为初创公司「账上没钱了」，为了生存，只能裁员。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">牛津大学的研究进一步证实了这一点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果将2022-2025年的「高科技职位招聘需求曲线」拿出来，就能发现，它与纳斯达克指数的走势惊人地重合，却与GPT-4等模型的发布时间点毫无相关性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7321274763135228\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1161\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1161\" data-height=\"850\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"411\" data-imgfileid=\"505184071\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5bc55861&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8Ewbic1IDCBd9MK8XNkqckd785VPK4N3ibwTolEX4VkrgHafTibM07P9ibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">利率上行，纳指下挫，招聘冻结——这完全符合宏观经济学模型，与「技术奇点」无关。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们必须承认，2020-2021年的抢人大战才是异常现象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那时，因为无限量化宽松，各类科技公司疯狂囤积人才，许多程序员拿着高薪实际上在做着重复的工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2022年的惨烈裁员潮，本质上是市场在暴力纠错——从「泡沫逻辑」回归到「商业常识」，而不是技术性淘汰。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">借刀杀人：一场蓄谋已久的「洗白」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如前文所述，裁员是宏观经济造成的，为什么所有公司都要把锅甩给AI？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">答案很简单：AI是资本市场上最好用的「遮羞布」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">分析师们给这种现象起了一个专属名词——「AI冗余洗白」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.37037037037037035\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"675\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"675\" data-height=\"250\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"208\" data-imgfileid=\"505184069\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=836851ca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8WopfpjxicvBhB7XvH4du1WtPhvMb1XXPUpMj6CTlnA8FKXf63Hdbp3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">假如你是一位纳斯达克上市公司的CEO。在这个资金寒冬里，你的业绩下滑，现金流紧张，必须要裁掉10%的员工来缩减开支。此时摆在你面前的有两份公关稿：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">低情商：因为我们前两年盲目扩张、管理不善，导致现在没钱了，被迫裁员。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-style:normal;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-style: normal;\">后果</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-style: normal;\">：股价暴跌，股东愤怒，董事会质疑你的能力，你可能比员工先卷铺盖走人。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">高情商：我们要All in AI，所以要进行战略性组织重构，优化冗余人力，打造更高效的AI驱动型企业。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-style: normal;\">后果</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：股价大涨，分析师为你鼓掌，称赞你拥有「壮士断腕」的远见卓识。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果你是CEO，你会选哪一个？答案不言自明。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来看看那些教科书级别的洗白案例：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Dropbox作为最早的「示范单位」，CEO Drew Houston在裁掉16%员工（500人）时，高调宣布：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI计算时代终于到来了，我们的下一阶段增长需要不同的技能组合。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669921875\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1024\" data-height=\"683\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505184072\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3985033e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8gia3IxN9zIJM6VSMIynjS1ka7aGMyibBzKTWawUC7vClExXkA3Vq7ibVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从物流巨头UPS裁员1.2万人，到各大科技公司如Amazon、Google的滚动式裁员，高管们在解释裁员理由时，「AI」一词的出现频率比「利润」还高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">多项行业调查显示，相当比例的高管承认，将裁员与AI挂钩是为了避免被市场视为「落伍者」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">老板们心里比谁都清楚，现阶段的AI根本干不了那一万名员工的活。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但在资本市场上，只要喊出AI的口号，裁员就不再是「衰退，而是进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，不是AI抢了你的工作，而是老板借着AI的名义，干掉了那些他早就想干掉、却一直找不到完美理由干掉的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">从暂时失业到永久出局</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然是经济周期作祟，那是不是只要等到降息、等到经济复苏，属于我们的那个「黄金时代」就会回来？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">遗憾的是，这才是本报告最残酷的真相。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">经济学中的「疤痕效应」，精准描述了我们此刻的困境：当2024-2025年宏观经济终于开始解冻时，不同行业的命运走向了截然相反的两端。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着美联储降息预期升温，非科技依赖型行业（如酒店、医疗、建筑）的需求曲线呈现「V型」或「U型」反弹，迅速回到了疫情前的水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1600\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"960\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"337\" data-imgfileid=\"505184070\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ec5510f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2GPr7lYETnzRaCjZCGVIo8EUdJSU9OfhRF9cQSztbibkB7LjRE5ZA4bjn4WbyOOsuNbgHa81cicjjg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">科技职位信息在 2022 年初之前后翻了一倍以上，但此后已全部回撤，截至 2025 年 7 月 11 日，较疫情前水平低 36%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，高AI暴露职位（文案、初级代码、翻译）的需求曲线却是绝望的「L型」——在经历了2022年的暴跌后，陷入结构性停滞，彻底与经济复苏脱钩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就解释了为什么你感觉「经济好像好了，但我的行业还没好」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因为企业在裁员后发现：虽然当初是因为没钱才裁员，但现在有了AI辅助，似乎确实不再需要把这些人招回来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Upwork和Fiverr等前沿市场的数据印证了这种「K型分化」：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下行线（K之下）：纯粹的翻译、纯粹的SEO文章写作、纯粹的初级Java外包，需求量几乎归零。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上行线（K之上）：标有「AI-Assisted」（AI辅助）、「Prompt Engineering」（提示词优化）或者是能驾驭AI的高级全栈工程师，薪资和需求都在飙升。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说美联储是突发性杀手，那么AI就是慢性毒药。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它确保了那些因经济周期消失的岗位，永远不会再回来。它把周期性的「临时失业」，变成了结构性的「永久淘汰」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2022年，老板因为穷开不起单；2026年，老板因为不需要，所以不开单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们耗费三年，将所有焦虑错投给了一个假想敌。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">却忽略了在资本寒冬里，真正的生存法则从来没变过：技术只是筹码，谁掌握了资本的流向，谁才拥有定义的权力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，别再问「AI何时会取代我」，这个问题已是过去式了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你应该问的是：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当所有的借口都被揭穿之后，除了那个随时可以被量化的自己，你手里还有没有底牌？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://the-decoder.com/new-study-disrupts-the-narrative-that-chatgpts-launch-triggered-a-job-decline/\" target=\"_blank\">https://the-decoder.com/new-study-disrupts-the-narrative-that-chatgpts-launch-triggered-a-job-decline/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.02554\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.02554</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.unite.ai/jobs-at-risk-from-ai-were-already-declining-before-chatgpt-launched/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.unite.ai/jobs-at-risk-from-ai-were-already-declining-before-chatgpt-launched/</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/technology/3751933-tech-and-ai-exposed-workers-hit-by-downturn-before-generative-ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.devdiscourse.com/article/technology/3751933-tech-and-ai-exposed-workers-hit-by-downturn-before-generative-ai</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "牛津大学研究揭示，2022 年科技行业大裁员本质上是美联储加息引发的宏观经济周期性纠错，而非 AI 取代人力，AI 仅被资本用作掩盖管理失误的“遮羞布”。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "牛津大学研究揭示，2022 年科技行业大裁员本质上是美联储加息引发的宏观经济周期性纠错，而非 AI 取代人力，AI 仅被资本用作掩盖管理失误的“遮羞布”。",
  "summary": "本文基于牛津大学和基尔世界经济研究所的最新实证研究，深度复盘了过去三年的科技行业裁员潮。研究发现，早在 ChatGPT 发布半年前，高科技岗位的招聘需求已出现断崖式下跌，这与美联储暴力加息导致的风险投资缩减高度相关，而非技术性替代。文章指出，企业高管利用“AI 冗余洗白”策略，将管理不善导致的裁员包装成拥抱 AI 的战略转型，以维护股价。然而，虽然 AI 不是裁员的元凶，但它产生的“疤痕效应”使得相关岗位在经济复苏中呈现“L 型”停滞，导致周期性失业演变为结构性永久淘汰。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "2022 年的科技行业大裁员并非由 AI 引发，而是宏观经济周期的暴力纠错。",
      "explanation": "数据显示高 AI 暴露职业的失业风险在 ChatGPT 发布前已远超其他行业，其招聘曲线与纳斯达克指数重合，而非模型发布时间点。"
    },
    {
      "point": "资本市场存在“AI 冗余洗白”现象，将裁员作为战略进化的伪装。",
      "explanation": "CEO 们倾向于将因资金链紧张导致的裁员解释为“All in AI”的组织重构，以此获得分析师认可并推高股价，掩盖管理失误。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 虽然不是裁员的元凶，却导致了岗位的“永久性消失”。",
      "explanation": "在经济复苏期，非科技岗位呈 V 型反弹，而高 AI 暴露岗位因企业发现 AI 可辅助替代部分职能，需求呈 L 型停滞，造成结构性淘汰。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "周期性缩编被伪装成技术性迭代，AI 替资本背了三年的锅，直到今天真相才被彻底复位。",
    "受害者是按照行业资金充裕度划定的，而不是‘是否能被 AI 替代’。",
    "老板们心里比谁都清楚，现阶段的 AI 根本干不了那一万名员工的活。但在资本市场上，只要喊出 AI 的口号，裁员就不再是衰退，而是进化。",
    "如果说美联储是突发性杀手，那么 AI 就是慢性毒药。它把周期性的‘临时失业’，变成了结构性的‘永久淘汰’。"
  ],
